She defies all odds and gender stereotypes about what women can and can’t do. If you haven’t watched it already make sure you check it out! 🙌🏾

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dhar Mann on June 09, 2021 tagging @kellansworld, and @dharmannstudios. May be an image of 1 person, balloon and outdoors.

node.text:
20 BILLION VIEWS?!? I remember struggling to break even 1,000 views when I began making videos 3 years ago. I’d refresh, refresh, refresh hoping to see that comma, but I rarely did 😞😂

All I can say is I’m so so grateful for all of the support! None of this would be possible without my amazing @dharmannstudios team and of course my incredible #DharMannFam! I honestly believe God blessed us with this success because our positive content was needed in a world that’s full of so much negativity 🙏🏽❤️ 

Knowing we’re making a difference in people’s lives is what makes the long nights and early mornings worth it every day. Never in a million years could I have imagined making a living doing something I love so much. I’m so excited to show you guys what’s to come... we’re barely getting started!!!

And please remember... we’re not just telling stories, we’re changing lives!!! And when you share my videos you’re helping to change lives too ❤️💫

I appreciate you watching and I’ll see you in the next video 😉
